resources.string:
1. If no network was found, and you aren't using the location help, connect manually to the device network and restart the process;
2. If no network was found and you art using the location help, certify the location (Location/GPS) is turned on. If doesn't, turn it on and restart the process;
3. If the device isn't creating any network (LED is off), restart the process and press the reset button of the device again;
4. The network created by the device is the tag 'DISP_' followed by the MAC of the device;
5. The device MAC can be found in a label sticked on it;
